      <title>美国港口谈判启动 以避免罢工扰乱经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-port-talks-kick-off-in-bid-to-avoid-economy-disrupting-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表东部和墨西哥湾沿岸码头工人的工会于周三在新泽西州举行为期两天的会议，与港口雇主讨论工资要求，否则罢工将扰乱从休斯顿到波士顿的海上贸易门户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-port-talks-kick-off-in-bid-to-avoid-economy-disrupting-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
